<i>Come to 43-87. Sajiro-gil.</i>

25
00:01:23.248 --> 00:01:24.999
<i>Be here within 30 minutes.</i>

26
00:01:25.083 --> 00:01:27.585
<i>If I don't get my one billion won.
consider your wife dead.</i>

27
00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:29.796
